{"type": "article", "id": 29641, "title": "英伦风食物包装", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-14T23:02:22Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 37, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160714231238XvG6WqcTg3jt5QyO.jpeg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>为了在国际市场上吸引更多顾客的关注，Mr Stanley 最近委托 <a href=\"http://nikandcarole.co.uk/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Nik and Carole</a> 为旗下的食品重新设计了一组包装，将英伦风情与各类异域元素融合在了 Stanley 先生的“旅程”当中。装有饼干的铁盒上采用红黑蓝三色印上了双层巴士的插画，复古的画风也帮助强调了品牌悠久的历史。两种糖果则采用了纸盒包装，标志性的大本钟以及电话亭搭配经典的字体与图案，排版简洁明了又不失趣味。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607142334081iAIQEhb8XCnRFYZ.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.708000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160714233409VvSDjebNPtlU4EY8.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160714233409pAQMEHt1PXmTOb67.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.708000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160714233410wnZkVWctRHNQPM3o.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.708000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}